caption.title: SD Bioline Dengue Duo NS1 test results do not correlate with WBC and PLT (Lao PDR DF patients).
caption.p: WBC (A) and PLT counts (B) measured in acute phase serum samples from 92 patients with a PCR-confirmed DENV infection. Dashed lines indicate reference values. Open/filled circles represent samples tested negative/positive in the SD Bioline Dengue Duo NS1 test. (C) Tabular summary of results. Statistical testing was performed using Fisherâ€™s exact test (two-sided), ns: not significant.
